c: 48
v: 16
t: "Iti (Muhammad (SAW)) kuvagari vemugwenga avo vakasara: “Muchava munokokwa kuti murwe nevanhu vane simba rakawanda, mucharwa navo kana kuti vachizvipira (kana zvadaro movatorera). Kana mukateerera, Allah vachakupai mubairo wakanaka. Asi kana mukafuratira sekufuratira kwamakamboita mushure, vachakutongai nemutongo wakaomarara.”"